<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Paulus von Elm und Dietz d. J. von Thüngen zu Schernau</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Freilassung der Armleute zu Hilpertshof des Kaspar Wernitzer, Bürger zu Nürnberg, und um Herausgabe ihrer Habe.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_516" id="257v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_516_r1l15"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Paulus von Elm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_516_r1l16">vnd Dyecʒen von Tungen <expan>Ju<ex>ni</ex><hi rend="sup">or</hi></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_516_r1l14">bed cʒu Schernaw </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_516_r1l17"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her Paulus vnd Dẏecʒ Vns iſt von Caſpar <expan>wernicʒ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_516_line_1576349304635_3974">vnſers burgers wegen fürgelegt worden / vvie Jr <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_516_r1l24">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan></del> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> burger ſeinen Armman 
<add><ab facs="#facs_516_r1l20">vnd <expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan> ſun </ab></add> vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough">hinterſeſſen </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_516_line_1576349322636_3984">kneht </ab></add> auf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_516_r1l25">ſeinem hof cʒu Hilperſhofen gefangen vnd Jn Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough">ſein </del> habe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_516_r1l26">genomen habt / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough">den </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_516_line_1576349346377_4003">die </ab></add> <expan>ſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ vnſers <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_516_r1l30">Arm 
<del rend="strikethrough">man </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_516_r1l29">leute </ab></add> ledig vnd Jn 
<add><l>Jr</l></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> ſein </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_516_line_1576349349760_4008">
<del rend="strikethrough">vnd Jr</del></ab></add> habe <expan>wıdergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet / Als etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_516_r1l31">Das wöllen etc . <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_516" id="257v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Paulus von Elm und Dyeczen von Tungen
                                <expan>ju<ex>ni</ex><hi rend="sup">or</hi></expan>, bed czu Schernaw
                    </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her Paulus und Dyecz, uns ist von Caspar
                                <expan>Wernicz<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, unsers burgers, wegen fürgelegt
                        worden, wie ir <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> burger seinen armman <add>und
                                    <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan> sun</add> und <add>kneht</add>
                        auf seinem hof czu Hilpershofen gefangen und in ir habe genomen habt.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus,</ex></expan> daz ir
                                <add>die</add><expan>selb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> unsers
                                <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> arm <add>leute</add> ledig und in
                            <add>ir</add> habe <expan>widergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet. Als etc.
                        Das wöllen etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um.</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
</div></body>
